      <h3 class="fancy-underline">What Vancooler Does</h3>
      <p>
        We are developing a web application that recommends locations and
        suitable social activities based on the level of shade at each place.
        Our goal is to help users enjoy outdoor experiences while staying
        comfortable during hot weather.
      </p>
