        <li class="list-group-item">Activity suggestions around each place</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">Weather-aware planning for hot days</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">Simple and user-friendly interface</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          Focus on comfort and outdoor safety during hot days
        </li>
